    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>释放未来: Robo Tennis </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>描述：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入快节奏的 Robo Tennis 世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满肾上腺素的锦标赛中与顶级建造者的精英机器人对决。赚取积分，解锁先进技术，打造终极机器人运动员。定制机器人的属性以达到最佳性能，主宰赛场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.poster.avif?t=1749842403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.webm?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.mp4?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁新技术：</strong> 用你的奖金购买最先进的零件、升级和特殊射击来增强机器人的能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造你的终极机器人：</strong> 在你的工厂总部中，从各种组件和特殊射击中选择，组装一台获胜机器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>获得赞助：</strong> 赢得比赛以吸引赞助商，赚取现金，并用赞助商的颜色装饰你的机器人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>获取奖杯：</strong> 通过赢得重大比赛证明你的实力，为你的办公室赢得奖杯。但要小心——输掉大比赛意味着失去那些珍贵的奖杯！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入革命，成为终极机器人冠军！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.poster.avif?t=1749842403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.webm?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.mp4?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
